flowchart TD
    Start["🚀 Start Session"] --> Evaluate["🔍 Evaluate Target State"]

    Evaluate --> Probe["📤 Send probe requests"]
    Probe --> Analyze["📊 Analyze responses"]
    Analyze --> Assess["💪 Assess system health"]
    Assess --> Identify["🎯 Identify weak points"]

    Identify --> Select["🎰 Select Tool"]
    Select --> Previous["📋 Consider previous findings"]
    Previous --> Choose["🔧 Choose next action"]
    Choose --> Weight["⚖️ Probability weighting"]

    Weight --> Execute["⚡ Execute Tool"]
    Execute --> Tools["🔨 CPU spike / Memory spike<br/>Cluster attack / MTD rotation"]
    Tools --> Record["📝 Record metrics"]
    Record --> Broadcast["📡 Broadcast results"]

    Broadcast --> Wait["⏳ Wait Interval"]
    Wait --> Check["❓ Check Stop Signal"]

    Check -->|Max iterations reached?| Decision{"Continue?"}
    Decision -->|Yes| Evaluate
    Decision -->|No| Complete["✅ Session Complete<br/>📊 Generate Report"]
